      <title>移民帮助美国就业增长速度超过鲍威尔的速度限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/immigration-helps-us-jobs-grow-faster-than-powell-s-speed-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于移民增加，美国就业市场今年可能会再次大幅升温，超出美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）认为的长期可持续水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/immigration-helps-us-jobs-grow-faster-than-powell-s-speed-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国银行第四季度不良房地产贷款激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/german-banks-saw-soured-property-loans-surge-in-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国银行发现，第四季度难以偿还商业地产贷款的客户数量大幅增加，因为该行业面临着更高的利率以及因疫情而加剧的消费者行为转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/german-banks-saw-soured-property-loans-surge-in-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 09:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
