      <title>拉加德首次降息后，美联储的长期阴影将落在欧洲央行身上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/long-shadow-of-the-fed-shows-limits-of-ecb-talk-of-independence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行坚称，在准备首先开始降息时，不会接受美联储的任何暗示——但其随后的政策路径很可能会受到美国发生的情况的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/long-shadow-of-the-fed-shows-limits-of-ecb-talk-of-independence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
